            . I am servant to 
               <persName id="t18220911-328-person2901">
                  Peter 
                  Jones
               <interp inst="t18220911-328-person2901" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-328-person2901" type="given" value="Peter"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-328-person2901" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 19th of September, the prisoner came in to buy a cheese - I saw him take two up, put one under his arm, and gave me the other to weigh, and while I was weighing it; he put the other in his basket. My master came up, and he was going out. I called to him, ran out, and brought him back with it in his basket - he begged of me to let him go.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220911-328-person2902">
                  PETER 
                  JONES
