                     <interp inst="t18220911-328-person2902" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep the shop. I secured him, and found this cheese in his basket.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I went to buy some scrapings, and had this cheese weighed.</p>
